{"tid":356328,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九寨溝直擊】震後景區今非昔比 火花海變泥坑如置身月球表面","createTime":"2017-08-12T03:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T16:27:03.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96e7de6efd7f5be342bb43b1ded8952e7233ad8f","tid":356328,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"完了吧如沒意外，入面散撚晒，可能要等十幾年先有一批新海子地貌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170812/57071254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170812%2F57071254&d=OqD2C0xP3Ur7qn00Z6%2FwtQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=5fded4fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170812%2F57071254&h=b7d67ce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170812/57071254</a><br />\n<br />\n 四川九寨溝景區自地震後無限期關閉，除因景區內仍有落石危險外，有部份景點已今非昔比，或需大改造才能重新開放。<br />\n <br />\n記者抵達蘆葦海後即循山邊棧道前往各景點視察，首個景點蘆葦海雖看似無礙，但臨近山邊的棧道多段均被落石及山泥沖斷，行走相當困難，大批落石被沖到蘆葦海，沿棧道一側的蘆葦林大部份被壓扁。<br />\n<br />\n循棧道再往火花海方向走，棧道情況亦不理想，但最令人震驚的是原本滿水的火花海，現在只剩下一個多個泥坑，坑內只餘小量溝水，仿如置身月球表面，日後或可改名為火花坑吸引遊客。<br />\n<br />\n因連接火花海與公路的橋已消失，記者沿棧道繼續深入樹正群海，樹正瀑布等景點，發現除棧道部份受損外，景點並無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n惟記者再沿棧道往犀牛海及諾日朗瀑布時，汛水現棧道基本上已不成形，全段完全塌方，無法行走唯有橫渡溝水往公路方向再前進。<br />\n<br />\n公路情況亦非理想，多處出現塌方，路上滿佈沙石，最終《蘋果》記者抵達諾日朗瀑布，發現瀑布已無當時拍攝《西遊記》時的美景，首先瀑布有部份已無降水乾枯，剩餘有降水的部份則變成激流，美景震後變質，或許難以復原。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者 廖怡德 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502471102_2759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170812%2Flarge%2F1502471102_2759.jpg&h=06b66e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502468749_aa49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170812%2Flarge%2F1502468749_aa49.jpg&h=c2d916e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502468744_164d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170812%2Flarge%2F1502468744_164d.jpg&h=68a0d09f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502468754_f8e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170812%2Flarge%2F1502468754_f8e2.jpg&h=4c836689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502468755_dd2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170812%2Flarge%2F1502468755_dd2c.jpg&h=e5eebfec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502469082_a510.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170812%2Flarge%2F1502469082_a510.jpg&h=dfabdeb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502468757_f21c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170812%2Flarge%2F1502468757_f21c.jpg&h=505979ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502468759_07a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170812%2Flarge%2F1502468759_07a1.jpg&h=b9cc1cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502468751_e1a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F201